<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٣٣٠ - حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5638">مُحَمَّدٌ: </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4085">عَبْدُ الْوَهَّابِ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/7242">يُونُسُ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1389">الْحَسَنِ </a>قَالَ: <span class="c2">«زَوَّجَ مَعْقِلٌ أُخْتَهُ فَطَلَّقَهَا تَطْلِيقَةً.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>